Main Content Region



Community Resources









The Division of Student Affairs supports the CSUSB community, which consists of students and their families, as well as staff members within Student Affairs. Use these pages to find resources for each group.




Find Resources





For Students
Student Affairs engages and supports CSUSB students through its many departments, programs, and services. Explore Student Affairs' resources for students.
Student Resources




For Parents and Families
Parents and families are an important part of the CSUSB community. Student Affairs offers several resources for parents and families to help new students, returning students and their families with the college transition and growth.
Parent and Family Resources






For Student Affairs Staff
Staff within the Division of Student Affairs can find information about division activities and professional development opportunities.
Student Affairs Resources
